<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="laughter-n">laughter <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lɑːftə(r)/    美 /'læftər/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>笑；笑声：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Laughter is good for your health! 
笑有益于身体健康！</p><footer>译林⑥ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Laughter burst from the crowd. 
人群中爆发出笑声。</p><footer>2009 湖南</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="burst-into-laughter">burst into laughter</h3>
<p>1.<strong>突然大笑起来</strong>  </p></div>